description:
IKIO is a leading manufacturer of energy-efficient LED lighting solutions for Commercial, Industrial, Residential, Hazloc, and Solar applications. We have been delivering high-quality products that meet the highest standards of performance, durability, and design.

Operating in the USA since 2014, with our headquarters in Indianapolis, Indiana, and over 30+ years of industry experience worldwide. We have strategically located distribution centers across USA. We cater to a wide range of customers, including Hospitality, Retail Stores, Offices, Warehouses, Manufacturing Facilities, Schools, Hospitals, and more.

We are passionate about turning your lighting vision into reality and innovating and maintaining solutions that drive our industry forward.
